            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "An MCD trade licence is renewed online through the MCD portal before it expires, with the previous licence, property tax receipt, proof of premises and the renewal fee. Renewal is normally annual, and a lapsed licence attracts a late fee plus the risk of sealing of the premises. The renewal fee is booked as rates and taxes in the profit and loss account."
          }
